{"tid":2305650,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[新詩]《十二》","createTime":"2020-11-29T23:03:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T15:36:56.000Z","uid":262389,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ce818264ce3f0324ccfb127306fcc365c673aa87","tid":2305650,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T23:03:34.000Z","msg":"《十二》<br />\n<br />\n十二<br />\n是生肖，是時辰；是圖騰，是記號<br />\n在我眼中是卧虎藏龍，生不逢時<br />\n在你眼中是豬狗不如，不識時務<br />\n是族魂的離散，是時代的烙印<br />\n是頂天立地的志，是刻不容緩的痛<br />\n是龍游淺水，是代罪羔羊<br />\n是時不予待，是年輕有罪<br />\n<br />\n十二<br />\n是星座，是門徒；是命運，是信念<br />\n在我眼中是純如白羊，善良友愛<br />\n在你眼中是毒蠍心腸，背叛貪婪<br />\n是弄人的悲劇，是信仰的崩壞<br />\n是良知散失的痛，是命途自決的志<br />\n是吉兇難料，是禍不單行<br />\n是信者失救，是自由有罪"},{"pid":"f762c80948350d8d35472666f0c93d65e5ae03e6","tid":2305650,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T23:18:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"af71f2f55d7c98cdaaa23015fea29c7b6407c4d8","tid":2305650,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T23:21:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"06a2bd6ad188c3792ef992026e910220889e68ff","tid":2305650,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T23:28:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6f92c8d3eed0428e287b26d1c51c570c6c109398","tid":2305650,"uid":280525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T23:48:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf0cb5539585f538ea6d76afdb5d5a842b066953","tid":2305650,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T00:07:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b9d5d920a2fa1fd3af3b603b75bc3af81f5fb339","tid":2305650,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T00:14:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c63ef265826ea4e7a1fbfa0b9709d0be71c6aed4","tid":2305650,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0